2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Benh_ga_nham_mat_chay_nuoc_mat_la_gi\" >B\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Trieu_chung_cho_thay_ga_nham_mat_chay_nuoc_mat\" >Tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Mat_ga_nhin_kem\" >M\u1eaft g\u00e0 nh\u00ecn k\u00e9m<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Mat_ga_bi_chay_nuoc\" >M\u1eaft g\u00e0 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Chay_nuoc_mat_co_bot\" >Ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u00f3 b\u1ecdt<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Nguyen_nhan_gay_benh_khien_ga_nham_mat_chay_nuoc_mat\" >Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y b\u1ec7nh khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Cach_chua_ga_nham_mat_chay_nuoc_mat_dut_diem\" >C\u00e1ch ch\u1eefa g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Bien_phap_ngan_nguoi_benh_ga_chay_nuoc_mat\" >Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ng\u0103n ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-nham-mat-chay-nuoc-mat\/ \u200e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i>G\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/i><\/a><i> l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ec7nh th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi n\u00f4ng d\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c s\u01b0 k\u00ea. G\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111au m\u1eaft ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi, n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c b\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y ra sao. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay t\u1ea1i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sv368<\/a> nh\u00e9!\u00a0<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Benh_ga_nham_mat_chay_nuoc_mat_la_gi\"><\/span><b>B\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u00e0 b\u1ecb nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ec7nh th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p \u1edf g\u00e0. N\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i gia c\u1ea7m x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb s\u1edbm b\u1ec7nh k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. Tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ec7nh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 b\u1ecb s\u01b0ng m\u1eaft, s\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lan sang c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e2u, m\u1eaft g\u00e0 s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft s\u1ebd ch\u1ea3y ra b\u1ecdt tr\u1eafng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Trieu_chung_cho_thay_ga_nham_mat_chay_nuoc_mat\"><\/span><b>Tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u00e0 b\u1ecb nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y b\u1eb1ng m\u1eaft th\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mat_ga_nhin_kem\"><\/span><b>M\u1eaft g\u00e0 nh\u00ecn k\u00e9m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u00fang ta r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c \u1edf g\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eaft th\u00ec th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 m\u1eaft g\u00e0. N\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 y\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c ch\u1eadm th\u00ec th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m. N\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1t th\u00ec g\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mat_ga_bi_chay_nuoc\"><\/span><b>M\u1eaft g\u00e0 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ta nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 l\u00fac khi n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y \u01b0\u1edbt, ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ra ngo\u00e0i. Trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, g\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eaft. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ngay, g\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u00a0 b\u1ecb m\u00f9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chay_nuoc_mat_co_bot\"><\/span><b>Ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u00f3 b\u1ecdt<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u1eaft g\u00e0 s\u01b0ng t\u1ea5y, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1eaft c\u00f3 b\u1ecb s\u01b0ng hay kh\u00f4ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3220\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3220\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3220 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-15.jpg\" alt=\"Tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-15.jpg?v=1709381606 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-15-300x150.jpg?v=1709381606 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-15-768x384.jpg?v=1709381606 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3220\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nguyen_nhan_gay_benh_khien_ga_nham_mat_chay_nuoc_mat\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y b\u1ec7nh khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ec7nh ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u1edf g\u00e0, nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 do vi khu\u1ea9n Gr(-) Haemophilillus paragallinarum g\u00e2y ra. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, b\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y\u00a0 kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn giai \u0111o\u1ea1n hay \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a g\u00e0. Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c vi khu\u1ea9n n\u00eau tr\u00ean, c\u00f2n c\u00f3\u00a0 nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, bao g\u1ed3m:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho vi khu\u1ea9n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1\u00a0 m\u1eaft c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed g\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 CO2, H2S, NH2 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eaft v\u00e0 h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p \u1edf g\u00e0.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u00e0 nu\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i gia c\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea9y giun cho g\u00e0. N\u1ebfu nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 giun s\u00e1n th\u00ec t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 l\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m r\u1ea5t cao. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e2y truy\u1ec1n qua th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m, n\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed v\u00e0 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu g\u00e0 nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t con g\u00e0 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh g\u00e3i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f9ng m\u1eaft.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3221\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3221\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3221 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-15.jpg\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y b\u1ec7nh khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-15.jpg?v=1709381607 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-15-300x150.jpg?v=1709381607 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-15-768x384.jpg?v=1709381607 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3221\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y b\u1ec7nh khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_chua_ga_nham_mat_chay_nuoc_mat_dut_diem\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u1eefa g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n b\u1ec7nh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i gia c\u1ea7m ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn\u00a0 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c b\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft n\u00e0y.\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi ch\u1eefa b\u1ec7nh cho <\/span><b>g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e0 b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u1eefa b\u1ec7nh nhanh h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u00e0n g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu m\u1eaft g\u00e0 b\u1ecb s\u01b0ng ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc do th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1i pha lo\u00e3ng. Ti\u1ebfp theo, v\u1ec7 sinh quanh m\u1eaft g\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra n\u00ean mua m\u1ed9t \u1ed1ng tetraxylin v\u00e0 b\u00f4i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c cho g\u00e0 trong 2-3 ng\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng t\u1ea5y v\u00e0 ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u1edf g\u00e0.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh n\u1eb7ng, h\u00e3y ti\u00eam cho n\u00f3 li\u1ec1u Tylosin. Li\u1ec1u khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 2,5ml m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n ti\u00eam h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n g\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00f4n tr\u00f9ng trong m\u1eaft, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n mua thu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111u\u1ed5i ch\u00fang. Sau \u0111\u00f3 cho g\u00e0 u\u1ed1ng levamisole theo li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi tr\u00ean bao b\u00ec. Theo d\u00f5i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u0103ng gi\u1ea3m li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thu\u1ed1c cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3222\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3222\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3222 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-15.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1eefa g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-15.jpg?v=1709381608 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-15-300x150.jpg?v=1709381608 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-15-768x384.jpg?v=1709381608 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3222\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ch\u1eefa g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bien_phap_ngan_nguoi_benh_ga_chay_nuoc_mat\"><\/span><b>Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ng\u0103n ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft b\u1ecb ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p \u1edf g\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p bao g\u1ed3m:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p chu\u1ed3ng tr\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 phun v\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c kh\u1eed tr\u00f9ng. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 di\u1ec7t vi tr\u00f9ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea7n cung c\u1ea5p cho g\u00e0 nh\u1eefng vitamin, kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ea7n \u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i h\u00e3y t\u0103ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 cho g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u00e3y t\u1ea9y giun \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3225\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3225\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3225 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-5.jpg\" alt=\"Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ng\u0103n ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-5.jpg?v=1709382119 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-5-300x150.jpg?v=1709382119 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-5-768x384.jpg?v=1709382119 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3225\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ng\u0103n ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b><i>G\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf g\u00e0. Anh em h\u00e3y truy c\u1eadp trang <\/span><\/i><a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\"><b><i>Sv368<\/i><\/b><\/a><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ngay \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecdc th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch kh\u00e1c nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>G\u00e0 nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ec7nh th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi n\u00f4ng d\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c s\u01b0 k\u00ea. G\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111au m\u1eaft ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi, n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3222,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2181","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-da-ga"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/